name: London views - 03 - Hackney Central to Homerton on 19/05/2021
description: Music part “2021 06” produced in May 2021 at GBL Studios in London, UK. Video filmed on May 19th 2021 in the AM on the Overground train from Hackney Central to Homerton, still in London, UK. Execution and editing by Matteo Manzini @matteomanzini__ (Twitter/Instagram). “Ordinary days in my city”. The first 3 editions of the piece are donated to #hicathon 05/2021.
